1
00:01:29,450 --> 00:01:31,380
From now on, the blood oath is void.

2
00:01:31,620 --> 00:01:35,160
You two no longer need to be bound by my obsession.

3
00:01:36,830 --> 00:01:38,160
No, A Ying.

4
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,620
Don't do anything stupid.

5
00:01:43,500 --> 00:01:45,830
Leave the rest to me.

6
00:01:49,250 --> 00:01:51,160
A Ying, come back!

7
00:01:51,750 --> 00:01:53,330
Come back!

8
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:14,700
A Deng.

9
00:02:15,250 --> 00:02:16,160
I'm fine.

10
00:02:16,450 --> 00:02:17,380
Lantern Master.

11
00:02:17,450 --> 00:02:21,160
I will stay in Wanyao Spirit Realm to monitor the divine stone.

12
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,490
If there's any anomaly,

13
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:24,370
I will inform you immediately.

14
00:02:24,950 --> 00:02:27,040
I leave the Spirit Realm in your hands.

15
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:29,450
A Ying, we will meet again.

16
00:02:45,829 --> 00:02:48,790
These evidences are enough to show the world.

17
00:02:51,250 --> 00:02:54,250
Tomorrow, I will take these evidences to the capital.

18
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:55,160
Jingchen,

19
00:02:55,829 --> 00:02:58,490
I'll have to trouble you with the court affairs.

20
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:08,330
A Deng, I'll go to the capital with you.

21
00:03:09,330 --> 00:03:10,330
Master used to say

22
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,620
healers shouldn't just stay in the valley.

23
00:03:12,620 --> 00:03:14,480
We must go out to save more people.

24
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:16,550
I can open a clinic in the capital

25
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:18,000
and pass down the medical skills.

26
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,910
Alright, let's go together.

27
00:03:26,620 --> 00:03:27,620
My lords,

28
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:30,329
these are all the evidences of the late emperor and the demon Qin Chong

29
00:03:30,329 --> 00:03:32,060
colluding to ruin the country.

30
00:03:32,910 --> 00:03:34,120
Every piece can be verified,

31
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,500
with absolutely no lies.

32
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:36,829
The late emperor was incompetent,

33
00:03:36,829 --> 00:03:38,090
colluded with demons,

34
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:40,040
and plunged the people into misery.

35
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:43,700
I propose to wipe out Qin Chong's remnants,

36
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:45,310
and enthrone a wise ruler

37
00:03:45,329 --> 00:03:46,860
to bring peace to the world.

38
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,329
We second the motion.

39
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:50,040
We second the motion.

40
00:04:05,620 --> 00:04:07,580
Thank you, Miss A Deng, for saving the people from misery

41
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:09,750
and protecting the loyal in times of danger.

42
00:04:09,750 --> 00:04:11,540
I swear to be diligent and love my people,

43
00:04:11,540 --> 00:04:12,410
protect the peace of the world,

44
00:04:12,410 --> 00:04:14,160
and never let the late emperor's mistakes repeat.

45
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:15,160
You flatter me, Your Majesty.

46
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:17,500
Protecting the mortal realm is my duty.

47
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:19,160
May Your Majesty guard this kingdom well

48
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,040
and protect the lights of thousands of homes.

49
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,370
General Xie's matter is finally settled.

50
00:04:23,450 --> 00:04:25,180
I have resigned to the emperor.

51
00:04:25,410 --> 00:04:26,370
He agreed.

52
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:06,700
Let's go.

53
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,530
Using my resentment to repair the demon core.

54
00:05:39,700 --> 00:05:40,540
Demon Lord,

55
00:05:41,409 --> 00:05:43,330
you really make the most of everything.

56
00:05:43,330 --> 00:05:45,540
You were so majestic 300 years ago.

57
00:05:45,540 --> 00:05:48,659
Now you are just firewood for me to temper the demon core.

58
00:05:48,659 --> 00:05:49,120
Qin Chong

59
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,750
was just a petty guardian,

60
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:52,200
yet he made you fight with all your might.

61
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:55,750
When the time comes, your dear sister will definitely find this place,

62
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:58,409
and she can perfectly mend the last crack for me.

63
00:05:58,659 --> 00:06:00,060
Don't you dare touch her.

64
00:06:01,370 --> 00:06:03,040
The day the demon core is repaired

65
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:05,900
is the day I personally descend to the mortal realm.

66
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:12,870
Sister,

67
00:06:13,830 --> 00:06:14,660
don't come.

68
00:06:18,620 --> 00:06:18,910
Oh,

69
00:06:18,910 --> 00:06:20,870
so this is Lantern Master Du.

70
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,540
Not quite what I imagined.

71
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:23,620
I am Lingdang,

72
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:26,200
a fresh spirit just out of the Wanyao Spirit Realm.

73
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,450
I will be following you from now on.

74
00:06:27,450 --> 00:06:28,380
You're welcome.

75
00:06:28,540 --> 00:06:30,340
What's with those expressions?

76
00:06:30,700 --> 00:06:33,100
Haven't you seen such a cute spirit before?

77
00:06:40,580 --> 00:06:42,450
What are you looking at, miss?

78
00:06:42,450 --> 00:06:44,040
My new life is great.

79
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,830
I used to always lose money in business.

80
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:47,409
Now I make a fortune every day.

81
00:06:47,409 --> 00:06:48,370
The Life Exchange Shop

82
00:06:48,370 --> 00:06:49,540
is really effective.
